-- Pirelli Raising Car, Light Truck Tire Prices by as Much as 7% in the U.S.
-- B y   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 2010-09-28T16:07:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-28/pirelli-raising-car-light-truck-tire-prices-by-as-much-as-7-in-the-u-s-.html
Pirelli & C. SpA said today it will
raise prices in the U.S. for car and light truck tire by as much
as 7 percent due to increasing raw material costs, according to
a statement distributed by the Italian exchange.  The new prices will be effective Dec. 1, it said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net  